---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="Andreos Klering - Product Engineering Leader & Builder. AI-driven cultures, teams that ship, transformation leadership.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-6 md:py-8 lg:py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      
      <!-- Mobile: Photo + Name header -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6 md:hidden">
        <img
          src="/images/andreos.jpg"
          alt="Andreos Klering"
          class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full object-cover"
        />
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            Andreos Klering
          </h1>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            Product Engineering Leader & Builder
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-16">
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <!-- Desktop: Name header -->
          <div class="hidden md:block">
            <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
              Andreos Klering
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
              Product Engineering Leader & Builder
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4 md:mb-6">
            I help engineering organizations build better—faster cycles, clearer decisions,
            cultures that actually ship. 20 years of building products, teams, and systems
            across fintech, SaaS, and payments.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4 md:mb-6">
            The game is changing. AI is collapsing build cycles from months to days.
            What used to be expensive is now cheap. The bottleneck has shifted from
            "can we build this?" to "should we?" I help teams navigate that shift.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8">
            Currently leading engineering at Nexar. Two-time founder.
            Builder at heart. Navigator of the AI transformation.
          </p>

          <!-- What I Believe - Desktop only, full width treatment -->
          <div class="hidden lg:block mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">What I Believe</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-amber-50 dark:from-orange-900/20 dark:to-amber-900/20 border border-orange-100 dark:border-orange-800/50">
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm mb-1">Simplicity is sophistication</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-xs leading-relaxed">The simpler the solution, the more powerful it becomes. Complexity feels smart but scales poorly.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 dark:from-blue-900/20 dark:to-indigo-900/20 border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800/50">
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm mb-1">Impact over output</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-xs leading-relaxed">Success isn't activity—it's outcomes. What changed because we built this?</p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 dark:from-emerald-900/20 dark:to-teal-900/20 border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50">
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm mb-1">Incentives drive outcomes</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-xs leading-relaxed">Systems create the behavior they reward. When something isn't working, look at the incentives.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-50 to-purple-50 dark:from-violet-900/20 dark:to-purple-900/20 border border-violet-100 dark:border-violet-800/50">
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm mb-1">AI is a paradigm shift</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-xs leading-relaxed">Not another tool—a transformation in how we build, lead, and create value. The future is human with AI.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- DOIS callout -->
          <div class="callout-box p-4 rounded-lg border mb-6 lg:mb-8">
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base">
              I co-run <a href="https://dois.one" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-sora font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-accent hover:underline">DOIS</a> with Thiago,
              where we publish experiments, notes, and opinions on engineering and building products.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Mobile: CTAs and links -->
          <div class="lg:hidden mb-6">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-4">
              <a href="/cv" class="btn-primary">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
                </svg>
                View CV
              </a>
              <a href="/writing" class="btn-secondary">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z"/>
                </svg>
                Read my writing
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/aklering" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-orange-600 dark:hover:text-accent transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
                LinkedIn
              </a>
              <a href="https://github.com/andkler" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-orange-600 dark:hover:text-accent transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
                GitHub
              </a>
              <a href="mailto:hey@andreos.dev" class="flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-orange-600 dark:hover:text-accent transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M0 3v18h24v-18h-24zm21.518 2l-9.518 7.713-9.518-7.713h19.036zm-19.518 14v-11.817l10 8.104 10-8.104v11.817h-20z"/></svg>
                Email
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Mobile: What I Believe -->
          <div class="lg:hidden mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What I Believe</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
              <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 border border-orange-100 dark:border-orange-800/50">
                <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xs">Simplicity is sophistication</p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-800/50">
                <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xs">Impact over output</p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-900/20 border border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-800/50">
                <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xs">Incentives drive outcomes</p>
              </div>
              <div class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-violet-50 dark:bg-violet-900/20 border border-violet-100 dark:border-violet-800/50">
                <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xs">AI is a paradigm shift</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Mobile: Compact info card -->
          <div class="md:hidden bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-4 mb-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm mb-4">
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Location</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Portugal</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Focus</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Fintech · SaaS · Scale-ups</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 italic">
              Builder at heart. AI-first leader. Ships things that matter.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Desktop Sidebar -->
        <div class="hidden lg:block lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-8">
            <div class="mb-6 flex justify-center">
              <img
                src="/images/andreos.jpg"
                alt="Andreos Klering"
                class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>

            <!-- CTAs -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 mb-6">
              <a href="/cv" class="btn-primary justify-center text-sm">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
                </svg>
                View CV
              </a>
              <a href="/writing" class="btn-secondary justify-center text-sm">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z"/>
                </svg>
                Read my writing
              </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Social Links -->
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-3 mb-6 pb-6 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/aklering" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-orange-600 dark:hover:text-accent hover:bg-orange-50 dark:hover:bg-orange-900/20 transition-colors" title="LinkedIn">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://github.com/andkler" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-orange-600 dark:hover:text-accent hover:bg-orange-50 dark:hover:bg-orange-900/20 transition-colors" title="GitHub">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="mailto:hey@andreos.dev" class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-orange-600 dark:hover:text-accent hover:bg-orange-50 dark:hover:bg-orange-900/20 transition-colors" title="Email">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M0 3v18h24v-18h-24zm21.518 2l-9.518 7.713-9.518-7.713h19.036zm-19.518 14v-11.817l10 8.104 10-8.104v11.817h-20z"/></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://dois.one" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-orange-600 dark:hover:text-accent hover:bg-orange-50 dark:hover:bg-orange-900/20 transition-colors font-sora font-bold text-xs flex items-center" title="DOIS">
                DOIS
              </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Quick facts -->
            <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Location</p>
                <p>Portugal</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Current role</p>
                <p>Head of Engineering @ Nexar</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Focus areas</p>
                <p>Fintech · SaaS · Payments · Scale-ups</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- What I care about -->
            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm mb-2">What I care about</p>
              <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-accent">→</span>
                  <span>AI-driven engineering cultures</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-accent">→</span>
                  <span>Autonomy with accountability</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-accent">→</span>
                  <span>Outcomes over output</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-accent">→</span>
                  <span>Simplicity at scale</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
